('- Default `family = gaussian(link = ""identity"")` — `glm()` with no `family` silently fits OLS (same as `lm`', 'From awesome-chatgpt-prompts community collection', 'but slower and with deviance-based output).', 'chatgpt', 1, ARRAY['community', 'chatgpt', 'prompts'], 'General use'),
('- Common families: `binomial(link = ""logit"")`', 'From awesome-chatgpt-prompts community collection', '`poisson(link = ""log"")`', 'chatgpt', 1, ARRAY['community', 'chatgpt', 'prompts'], 'General use'),
('- `weights` in `glm` means **prior weights** (not frequency weights) — for frequency weights', 'From awesome-chatgpt-prompts community collection', 'use the cbind trick or offset.', 'chatgpt', 1, ARRAY['community', 'chatgpt', 'prompts'], 'General use'),
('- `anova(glm_obj', 'From awesome-chatgpt-prompts community collection', 'test = ""Chisq"")` for deviance-based tests; `""F""` is invalid for non-Gaussian families.', 'chatgpt', 1, ARRAY['community', 'chatgpt', 'prompts'], 'General use'),
