('- `aov` is a wrapper around `lm` that stores extra info for balanced ANOVA. For unbalanced designs', 'From awesome-chatgpt-prompts community collection', 'Type I SS (sequential) are computed — order of terms matters.', 'chatgpt', 1, ARRAY['community', 'chatgpt', 'prompts'], 'General use'),
